params.sqlcmd: "select " +" TO_CHAR(M_CAL.\\"CAL_NO\\") as \\"CAL_NO\\", " +" M_CAL.\\"CAL_DATE\\" as \\"CAL_DATE\\", " +" M_CAL.\\"HOLIDAY_FLG\\" as \\"HOLIDAY_FLG\\", " +" M_CAL.\\"CAL_COMMENT\\" as \\"CAL_COMMENT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_CAL.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\") as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" M_ASP_CALENDAR.\\"SHIFT_CD\\" as \\"SHIFT_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_CAL, " +" M_ASP_CALENDAR " +"where " +" M_CAL.\\"CAL_NO\\" = TO_NUMBER(?) " +" and M_CAL.\\"CAL_DATE\\" LIKE ? " +" and M_ASP_CALENDAR.RES_CD(+) = M_CAL.CAL_NO " +" and M_ASP_CALENDAR.CALENDAR_DATE_CD(+) = M_CAL.CAL_DATE " +"order by " +" M_CAL.\\"CAL_DATE\\""
"select " +" TO_CHAR(M_CAL_H.\\"CAL_NO\\") as \\"CAL_NO\\", " +" M_CAL_H.\\"CAL_NAME\\" as \\"CAL_NAME\\" " +"from " +" M_CAL_H " +"where " +" M_CAL_H.\\"CAL_NO\\" = TO_NUMBER(?)"

"select " +" TO_CHAR(M_CAL.\\"CAL_NO\\") as \\"CAL_NO\\", " +" M_CAL.\\"CAL_DATE\\" as \\"CAL_DATE\\", " +" M_CAL.\\"HOLIDAY_FLG\\" as \\"HOLIDAY_FLG\\", " +" M_CAL.\\"CAL_COMMENT\\" as \\"CAL_COMMENT\\" " +"from " +" M_CAL " +"where " +" M_CAL.\\"CAL_NO\\" = TO_NUMBER(?) " +" and TO_DATE(M_CAL.\\"CAL_DATE\\") <= TO_DATE(?) " +" and TO_DATE(M_CAL.\\"CAL_DATE\\") >= TO_DATE(?) " +"order by " +" M_CAL.\\"CAL_DATE\\""
"update " +" M_CAL " +"set " +" \\"HOLIDAY_FLG\\" = ? " +"where " +" M_CAL.\\"CAL_NO\\" = TO_NUMBER(?) " +" and TO_DATE(M_CAL.\\"CAL_DATE\\") = TO_DATE(?)"
"update " +" M_CAL " +"set " +" \\"HOLIDAY_FLG\\" = ?, " +" \\"CAL_COMMENT\\" = ? " +"where " +" M_CAL.\\"CAL_NO\\" = TO_NUMBER(?) " +" and TO_DATE(M_CAL.\\"CAL_DATE\\") = TO_DATE(?)"

"select " +" TO_CHAR(T_CAL_BY_YEAR.\\"CAL_NO\\") as \\"CAL_NO\\", " +" T_CAL_BY_YEAR.\\"CAL_YEAR\\" as \\"CAL_YEAR\\", " +" T_CAL_BY_YEAR.\\"CAL_YEAR_HOLIDAY\\" as \\"CAL_YEAR_HOLIDAY\\" " +"from " +" T_CAL_BY_YEAR " +"where " +" T_CAL_BY_YEAR.\\"CAL_NO\\" = TO_NUMBER(?) " +" and T_CAL_BY_YEAR.\\"CAL_YEAR\\" = ?"

"select " +" TO_CHAR(M_CAL.\\"CAL_NO\\") as \\"CAL_NO\\", " +" M_CAL.\\"CAL_DATE\\" as \\"CAL_DATE\\", " +" M_CAL.\\"HOLIDAY_FLG\\" as \\"HOLIDAY_FLG\\", " +" M_CAL.\\"CAL_COMMENT\\" as \\"CAL_COMMENT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_CAL.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\") as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_CAL " +"where " +" M_CAL.\\"CAL_NO\\" = TO_NUMBER(?) " +" and TO_DATE(M_CAL.\\"CAL_DATE\\") = TO_DATE(?) " +"FOR UPDATE nowait"
"update " +" M_ASP_CALENDAR " +"set " +" SHIFT_CD = ? " +"where " +" RES_CD = ? " +" and TO_DATE(CALENDAR_DATE_CD) = TO_DATE(?)"
"insert into " +" M_ASP_CALENDAR(RES_CD, CALENDAR_DATE_CD, SHIFT_CD, SORTORDER, DEFAULT_QTY) " +"VALUES " +" (?, ?, ?, 1, 1)"
"select " +" CALENDAR_DATE_CD " +"from " +" M_ASP_CALENDAR " +"where " +" RES_CD = ? " +" and CALENDAR_DATE_CD = TO_DATE(?)"
